Name: Koleda
Desc: Use it to obtain the Agent or unlock the Agent's Mindscapes.
Desc2:
Snapshots from Koleda's daily life and from in combat, recording important moments before and after she became an Agent.
These images also provide insights into her fighting style and favorite weapons, helping to better understand her strengths.

Most are candid shots taken at the construction site, where the president can be seen unexpectedly caught in the middle of the hustle and bustle.
